Package: theoraizer
Type: Package
Title: Develop Theories using Large Language Models
Version: 1.3.1
Authors@R: person("Meike", "Waaijers", email = "m.waaijers@uva.nl",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Meike Waaijers <m.waaijers@uva.nl>
Description: Use Large Language Models (LLMs) to construct a coherent theory
  within the Causal Loop Diagram (CLD) framework. The theory consists of key
  variables and their causal relationships, and can be visually represented.
